codeText: public ExecutorThreadFactory(String poolName, UncaughtExceptionHandler exceptionHandler) {_		checkNotNull(poolName, "poolName")___		SecurityManager securityManager = System.getSecurityManager()__		this.group = (securityManager != null) ? securityManager.getThreadGroup() :_				Thread.currentThread().getThreadGroup()___		this.namePrefix = poolName + "-thread-"__		this.exceptionHandler = exceptionHandler__	}
